State Regulations

Pursuant to section
94
(8)
of the Public Officers Law, this Part
shall not apply to a record of the commission which pertains to investigation, law enforcement, confinement of persons in correctional facilities, or
supervision of persons pursuant to criminal conviction or court
order. Notes
